General.Name: Totalbanken A/S
General.Description: Totalbanken A/S provides various banking products and services to private households, and small and medium-sized enterprises in Denmark. The company offers deposit and payment accounts; housing and car loans; insurance, investment, and pension products; construction and operating financing; leasing of equipment; car leasing; mortgages; guarantees; credit and debit cards; and online and mobile banking services. It operates through branches on West Funen, as well as ErhvervsCenter; and Odense. The company was founded in 1911 and is headquartered in Aarup, Denmark.
